OL,3,CPolice warn visitors to 'stay well
OL,4,Caway' after landslide on beach
OL,6,FAuthorities have urged people to stay
OL,7,Faway from a beach in north Wales
OL,8,Ffollowing a cliff landslide.
OL,10,FThis is the latest incident at Nefyn
OL,11,Fbeach after previous landslips at the
OL,12,Fend of 2025 and start of this year.
OL,13,FThere has also been coastal issues at
OL,14,Fnearby Porthdinllaen.
OL,16,FNorth Wales Police has warned people
OL,17,Fto "stay well away" from the affected
OL,18,Farea. The incident is near to one of
OL,19,Fthe car parks next to the beach.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
