OL,3,CPolice warn visitors to 'stay well
OL,4,Caway' after landslide on beach
OL,6,FA spokesperson for North Wales Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Emergency services have been
OL,8,Falerted to a landslide on Nefyn beach,
OL,9,Fnear to the car park.
OL,11,F"We are advising anyone in the
OL,12,Fimmediate vicinity to stay well away
OL,13,Ffrom the affected area both above and
OL,14,Fon the beach, as more landslides may
OL,15,Foccur.
OL,17,F"Police, Coastguard and Local
OL,18,Fauthority colleagues will be assessing
OL,19,Fthe situation as a matter of urgency."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
