OL,3,CPolice warn visitors to 'stay well
OL,4,Caway' after landslide on beach
OL,6,FNefyn beach is prone to landslides as
OL,7,Fit is backed by steep, unstable
OL,8,Fcliffs. Evidence of previous landslips
OL,9,Fand subsequent underpinning work can
OL,10,Fbe seen all around.
OL,12,FA major slip in April 2021 left a 40-
OL,13,Fmetre wide gouge in the cliffs and
OL,14,Fhouses teetering on the edge.
OL,16,FIn January 2001, a series of slides
OL,17,Fswept two cars over the cliff and onto
OL,18,Fthe beach below, killing one of the
OL,19,Foccupants and seriously injuring
OL,20,Fanother.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
